embedvideo-load: Label for button to load the embedded video. $1 is the service name.
embedvideo-consent-privacy-notice-text: Privacy notice text. $1 is the service name.
embedvideo-service-bandcamp:
{{Optional}}
The name of an online music publishing service, https://bandcamp.com/ .
embedvideo-service-dailymotion:
{{Optional}}
Name of Dailymotion video streaming service, see https://www.dailymotion.com
embedvideo-service-deezer:
{{Optional}}
The name of the online Hi-Fi music streaming service, see https://deezer.com/
embedvideo-service-tidal:
{{Optional}}
The name of the online Hi-Fi music streaming service, see https://tidal.com/
embedvideo-service-localvideo: Label for local video file service.
embedvideo-error-missingparams: Error message for missing required parameters.
embedvideo-error-service: Error message for unrecognized video service. $1 is the service name.
embedvideo-error-id: Error message for bad video ID. $1 is the service name, $2 is the ID.
embedvideo-error-width: Error message for bad width parameter. $1 is the width value.
embedvideo-error-height: Error message for bad height parameter. $1 is the height value.
embedvideo-error-alignment: Error message for illegal alignment parameter. $1 is the alignment value.
embedvideo-error-valignment: Error message for illegal vertical alignment parameter. $1 is the valignment value.
embedvideo-error-urlargs: Error message for malformed URL arguments.
embedvideo-error-unknown: Error message for unknown error. $1 is the error details.
embedvideo-error-evp_deprecated: Error message indicating #evp parser function is deprecated.
embedvideo-error-container: Error message for invalid container parameter.
embedvideo-video-long-desc: Long description format for video. $1 is service, $2 is codec, $3 is length, $4 is width, $5 is height, $6 is overall description.
embedvideo-audio-long-desc: Long description format for audio. $1 is service, $2 is codec, $3 is length, $4 is overall description.
embedvideo-error-cantdecode_evu: Error message when video cannot be parsed. $1 is the input.
embedvideo-error-url-not-whitelisted: Error message when URL is not in whitelist.
apihelp-embedvideo-param-urlargs: API parameter description for URL arguments.
